{
  "stem": "10835.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They did not take us to a shelter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We remained in the factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But all the Nazi people went into a shelter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she had one of her epileptic seizures.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she dropped right in the mud and dirt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we were-- we felt good about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Anything bad that happened to them made us feel better.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Anyway, that was about the only air raid at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And it passed quickly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Then towards the end of the year, the beginning of 1945, we found out about the death march.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did we found-- find out?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were located when they were running-- when they were bringing people from the west to the east, and then people from the east to the west, we were like in the center.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one transport stopped at our camp overnight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we weren't allowed to go to the window to look.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, one of the women-- we were-- that time, we were located on the third floor of the factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one woman-- there were these little windows in the large one, these little tiny windows that you open as part of a large window.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A woman stuck her head out to see what's going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was shot dead right then and there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And these people being [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] chased back and forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one morning, a few girls, including me, were sent to the railroad station to clean up after the people were stopped there at the train.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we saw a lot of blood there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And once on the way from work, from the factory-- no, from the camp to the factory, we had to march under an overpass.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
